    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>seeded tortillas</strong> to a baking tray and put in the oven for 4-5 min or until they are beginning to crisp (the rest will be put in the oven later)</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pumpkin seeds</strong> and <strong>sesame seeds</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until toasted and beginning to pop, then remove from the heat</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk so they don't burn!</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
