    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the seeds are toasting, crush the <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing with the side of a knife and discard the skins</p><p>Cut the <strong>green chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon)</p><p>Trim 1 <span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and cut the<strong> pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p>",
